title: Conservation of Energy
text: Remember that energy must be conserved in our system.

title: Conservation of Energy
text: There is no final potential energy thus the equation we need to solve is the Kinetic Energy Inital $$+Potential$$ Energy Initial $$=$$ Kinetic Energy Final.

title: Solve
text: Solve for Vf where Vf is the final velocity: $$\frac{1}{2} {15}^2$$ + $$9.8\times20$$ $$=$$ $$\frac{1}{2} {Vf}^2$$.
